imdb.plot outline: Watch Sneek & The Geek to see contestants learn the probabilities behind trading as they compete for the $5,000 Grand Prize. Host Sonika Singh and Jacob "The Geek" Pearlman are two University of Chicago math whizzes who show you the theory behind the numbers, and why "smarts" rule. The brackets are filling up as we get closer to finding out who will win the $5000 grand prize. Sure, the bragging rights are priceless, but what you learn about probability is invaluable. We still aren't sure what a Sneek is, but we're glad she's here to help ferret out the the inner geek inside us all.
